01:08:52.175 --> 01:08:57.319 align:middle line:90%


01:08:57.319 --> 01:09:03.800 align:middle line:84%
My message for humanity is that
every single person can find

01:09:03.800 --> 01:09:08.450 align:middle line:84%
God within, can find
happiness within,

01:09:08.450 --> 01:09:12.680 align:middle line:84%
and that every
