01:09:24.964 --> 01:09:32.200 align:middle line:84%
and awaken to that divine,
pure, perfect, infinite quality

01:09:32.200 --> 01:09:33.770 align:middle line:90%
that's within you.

01:09:33.770 --> 01:09:36.540 align:middle line:90%
You have to help others.

01:09:36.540 --> 01:09:40.710 align:middle line:84%
In order to become
you life meaningful,

01:09:40.710 --> 01:09:42.689 align:middle line:90%
yo do something for others.

01:09:42.689 --> 01:09:46.571 align:middle line:84%
You do something for others
to help people around you,

01:09:46.571 --> 01:09:49.960 align:middle line:90%
