01:10:25.400 --> 01:10:27.660 align:middle line:84%
That is the most
important thing.

01:10:27.660 --> 01:10:32.090 align:middle line:10%
It's not to think about it,
to talk about, to pretend

01:10:32.090 --> 01:10:35.340 align:middle line:10%
