source, one great energy

01:10:59.180 --> 01:11:01.750 align:middle line:90%
moving through us all.

01:11:01.750 --> 01:11:05.730 align:middle line:90%
We are all children of one god.

01:11:05.730 --> 01:11:07.710 align:middle line:84%
Therefore, let's get
to know each other.

01:11:07.710 --> 01:11:11.721 align:middle line:84%
And instead of killing each
other, love each other,

01:11:11.721 --> 01:11:14.610 align:middle line:90%
