01:11:14.610 --> 01:11:18.560 align:middle line:84%
Every human being should
strive to know himself.

01:11:18.560 --> 01:11:21.860 align:middle line:84%
Not psychologically,
not intellectual,

01:11:21.860 --> 01:11:24.490 align:middle line:90%
